e":"article-journal","title":"Enantioselective total synthesis of (-)-erinacine B.","issued":{"date-parts":[[2007]]},"DOI":"10.1021/ol0628816","container-title":"Organic Letters","abstract":"The first enantioselective total synthesis of (−)-erinacine B has been achieved. Our approach features convergent construction of the 5-6-7 tricyclic cyathane core system via chiral building blocks prepared using asymmetric catalysis developed by us and highly stereoselective construction of all stereogenic centers in the aglycon.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Watanabe","given":"Hideaki","literal":""},{"family":"Watanabe","given":"Hideaki","literal":""},{"family":"Takano","given":"Masashi","literal":""},{"family":"Takano","given":"Masashi","literal":""},{"family":"Umino","given":"Akinori","literal":""},{"family":"Umino","given":"Akinori","literal":""},{"family":"Ito","given":"Toshiya","literal":""},{"family":"Ito","given":"Toshiya","literal":""},{"family":"Ishikawa","given":"Hiroyuki","literal":""},{"family":"Ishikawa","given":"Hiroyuki","literal":""},{"family":"Nakada","given":"Masahisa","literal":""},{"family":"Nakada","given":"Masahisa","literal":""}],"citation-key":"watanabe_enantioselective_2007","year":"2007","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Enantioselective total synthesis of (-)-erinacine B."],"author-links":["[[Author/Hideaki Watanabe]]","[[Author/Hideaki Watanabe]]","[[Author/Masashi Takano]]","[[Author/Masashi Takano]]","[[Author/Akinori Umino]]","[[Author/Akinori Umino]]","[[Author/Toshiya Ito]]","[[Author/Toshiya Ito]]","[[Author/Hiroyuki Ishikawa]]","[[Author/Hiroyuki Ishikawa]]","[[Author/Masahisa Nakada]]","[[Author/Masahisa Nakada]]"],"attachment":["[[biblib/watanabe_enantioselective_2007/watanabe_enantioselective_2007.pdf|PDF]]"],"related":[[]]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"prl31y","at":1774951892262}},"smart_blocks:Research/@watanabe_enantioselective_2007.md#---front